title: Punisher (001 - 016 & Franken-Castle 017 - 021) (2009 - 2010
description:
Punisher (001 - 016 & Franken-Castle 017 - 021) (2009 - 2010) (digital) (Minutemen-InnerDemons) 


Punisher Volume 7

Fourth mainstream ongoing series. The series is somewhat of a continuation of Frank's adventures in Punisher War Journal Vol.2 that stopped a month before this series started. Written by Rick Remender, following the Punisher in the wake of Dark Reign and his struggles with Norman Osborn. The series took a turn to the controversial with the "Franken-Castle" storyline. Beginning with issue #17, the series changes its title to Franken-Castle.
